    "eyebrow": "Case Study",
    "num": "20",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">20</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Case Study</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Native American Influence on Texican Frontier Life</h2><ul><li>Review of Comanche and Caddo roles in shaping Texican settlements</li><li>Impact on military strategies and cultural practices</li><li>Economic and social exchanges across cultural boundaries</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">This case study synthesizes Native American influences on Texican frontier life, highlighting the interplay of conflict, cooperation, and cultural blending. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s8\">[8]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s9\">[9]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Texican settlers adapted their fortifications and trade practices in response to Native American presence.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Evaluate how Native American interactions influenced Texican community development.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Separating Native influence from Texican cultural evolution.</p></div></div>",
